Package Manipulators

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChordConstructor
    Singleton class that constructs chords associated with given ChordEnum type.
    GeneralManipulator
    A singleton object which provides a series of methods for manipulating musical elements.
    IntervalConstructor
    Class following the singleton pattern which is used to construct intervals.
    ScaleConstructor
    A class that implements the singleton pattern.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ChordEnum
    The list of chord types.
    IntervalEnum
    A set of enum types representing various intervallic distances.
    ScaleModeEnum
    A list of enums representing different scale modes.
  • Exception Summary

    A class extending the Exception class which is thrown if a Key object's position is outside of the supported range.

    A class extending the RuntimeException class which is thrown if a Key object's position is outside of the supported range.
